message.text:
締切迫る！2015年第1回日本語能力試験(JLPT)、申し込み受付中！
もしまだならお早めに！日本での締切は4/30！
http://www.jlpt.jp/index.html

Register now!
Have you registered for the first Japanese-Language Proficiency Test (JLPT) in 2015? Check the deadline in your city and register soon!
http://www.jlpt.jp/e/index.html

今年もやってきました、第1回JLPTの季節！今年は7月5日開催予定です。
昨年12月の試験は、国内外で30万人以上が受験！
試験までまだ？もう？3ヶ月！
みなさん、頑張りましょ～。
（申し込みの締め切りは国や地域によって異なりますので、お気をつけください。）

JLPT season has come! The first JLPT this year will be held on July 5th.
In December last year, more than 300,000 people took the JLPT in Japan and overseas.
There are still? or only? three months left till the exam! 
Let's roll up our sleeves, everyone!

(Note:Application period varies by city. Please make sure to confirm with your local host institution.)

message.text:
The Japanese fiscal year begins in April, neither January nor September. 
School entrance, company entrance...this is the time "freshman" jump into their new world. 
Hence, entrance ceremonies were held all over Japan this week. 
The start of something new may be a little fluttering, but it's always nice to set yourself in a brand new frontline! 
Why not start learning Japanese with our Japanese in Anime & Manga Website? 
We've got all School vocabularies you can think of! 
http://anime-manga.jp/

message.text:
NOW OPEN !!!
Los Angels(U.S.):[Exhibition] Raku: The Cosmos in a Tea Bowl (until Sunday, June 7)
ロサンゼルス（米国）：｢樂-茶碗の中の宇宙｣展（6/7（日）まで）
http://www.jpf.go.jp/e/culture/exhibit/oversea/1503/03-01.html

The exhibition presents 450 years of Raku ware to be held at the Los Angeles County Museum of Art.
It was started in 450 years ago, 16th century, the Azuchi Momoyama period in Japan, when Samurai were still active! 
Feel the 450 year-history and tradition in live;)
--------------
樂焼450年の粋を集めた展覧会をロサンゼルス・カウンティ美術館で開催。

樂焼がうまれた450年前は、日本では桃山時代（16世紀）、まだ侍がいたころなんて...感慨深い。
450年の歴史と伝統をぜひ生で感じてください！
http://www.jpf.go.jp/j/culture/exhibit/oversea/1503/03-01.html
